@startuml
autonumber

box "Orchestration Layer" #LightCyan
participant "Camunda Engine" as Camunda
participant "Kong Gateway" as Kong
end box

box "Microservice Layer" #LightYellow
participant "Prosumer MS" as PMS
participant "Telemetry MS" as TMS
participant "Flexibility Event MS" as FlexMS
end box

box "Messaging Layer" #Thistle
queue "Kafka Topic:\nflexibility-offers" as KafkaFlex
end box

box "Persistence Layer" #LightGreen
database "AWS RDS" as AWSRDS
end box

== Orchestration & Data Gathering ==

Camunda -> Kong: Request active prosumers/assets
Kong -> PMS: GET /prosumers/active

PMS -> AWSRDS: JDBC SELECT Prosumers and Assets
AWSRDS --> PMS: ResultSet

PMS --> Kong: 200 OK\n{prosumerId, assetId}
Kong --> Camunda: 200 OK {prosumerId, assetId}

Camunda -> Kong: Request asset telemetry
Kong -> TMS: GET /telemetry/{assetId}

TMS -> AWSRDS: JDBC SELECT Telemetry for {assetId}
AWSRDS --> TMS: ResultSet

TMS --> Kong: 200 OK TelemetryDTO
Kong --> Camunda: 200 OK TelemetryDTO
== Flexibility Evaluation & Emission ==

Camunda -> Kong: Trigger Flexibility Evaluation POST \n/FlexibilityEvent/evaluate/{prosumerId}
note right of Camunda: Payload: TelemetryDTO
Kong -> FlexMS: Forward POST

FlexMS -> FlexMS: Apply Flexibility emission rules
note right of FlexMS
  If SoC > 90.0:
    eventType = "ARBITRAGE_SELL"
    recommendedAction = "DISCHARGE"
    Calculate Market Price & Incentive
  If SoC < 20.0:
    eventType = "BALANCING_UNAVAILABLE"
    recommendedAction = "UNAVAILABLE"
end note

FlexMS -> AWSRDS: INSERT INTO FlexibilityEvent\n(assetId, prosumerId, eventType, \nsoc_percent, recommendedAction... )
AWSRDS --> FlexMS: 200 OK (Generated ID)

FlexMS -> KafkaFlex: Publish to 'flexibility-offers'\n{"eventId":X, "assetId":Y, \n"prosumerId":Z, "eventType":"...",\n "recommendedAction":"...", ...}
KafkaFlex --> FlexMS: Ack

FlexMS --> Kong: 200 OK (FlexibilityEvent JSON)
Kong --> Camunda: 200 OK (Event Created)

== Asynchronous Consumption ==

loop Continuous Listening
   PMS -> KafkaFlex: Consume from flexibility-offers
   KafkaFlex -> PMS: JSON Event Payload
   note right of PMS: Process event (e.g., notify prosumer, update prosumer dashboard)
end
@enduml